OL,5,GSince the move to New Broadcasting
OL,6,GHouse in 2013, there seems to have been
OL,7,Gan endless supply of mishaps with the
OL,8,Grobotic cameras in the various BBC News
OL,9,Gstudios.
OL,11,FAlthough the type of glitch/operator
OL,12,Ferror follows a similar pattern on most
OL,13,Foccasions, there's a degree of
OL,14,Fcuriosity about how the presenter will
OL,15,Fhandle the situation.
OL,17,FAt the start of the 5.30am programme
OL,18,Ftoday, we had a slightly unusual strain
OL,19,Fof camera glitch.
