OL,5,FInitially, it looked as though the
OL,6,Fcamera was turning towards the catwalk,
OL,7,Fas expected, where presenter Victoria
OL,8,FValentine would link into the first
OL,9,Freport.
OL,11,FBut the camera immediately began to
OL,12,Fturn away from the catwalk and towards
OL,13,Fthe desk, leaving Victoria with no
OL,14,Fchoice but to abandon the catwalk and
OL,15,Fhead back to the desk.
OL,17,FHaving followed the camera back to the
OL,18,Fdesk, Victoria provided the link into
OL,19,Fthe lead story.
